# Generated self-hosted engine (issue #383): compiled from
# dart/self_host/engine.ball.pb through the Ball -> C# compiler by
# csharp/engine/tool. Kept out of git (like rust/engine/src/compiled_engine.rs
# and cpp's engine_rt.cpp) so the repo doesn't balloon and review isn't churned
# by a machine-emitted file; it is regenerated on demand and CI-side. It only
# participates in the build under `-p:SelfHost=true` (see engine/Ball.Engine.csproj).
engine/src/CompiledEngine.cs

# Generated self-hosted CLI core (issue #385): compiled from
# dart/self_host/cli.ball.json through the Ball -> C# compiler by
# csharp/cli/tool. Same reasoning as CompiledEngine.cs above. It only
# participates in the build under `-p:CliCore=true` (see cli/Ball.Cli.csproj).
cli/src/CompiledCli.cs
